        <a href="/best-golf-rangefinders-2026/">Best Rangefinders 2026</a>
        <a href="/best-golf-gps-watches/">Best GPS Watches</a>
        <a href="/best-golf-balls-2026/">Best Golf Balls 2026</a>
        <a href="/golf-ball-complete-guide/">Golf Ball Complete Guide</a>
        <a href="/golf-ball-compression-chart/">Ball Compression Chart</a>
        <a href="/best-golf-bags-2026/">Best Golf Bags 2026</a>
        <a href="/best-hybrid-clubs-2026/">Best Hybrids 2026</a>
        <a href="/best-golf-grips-2026/">Best Grips 2026</a>
        <a href="/best-wedges-for-beginners/">Best Wedges for Beginners</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <p style="font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold)">Golf Tech & Simulators</p>
        <a href="/golf-tech/">Golf Tech Hub</a>
