        <a href="/golf-simulator-room-dimensions-guide/">Room Dimensions Guide</a>
        <a href="/portable-golf-simulator-setup/">Portable Simulator Setup</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <p style="font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--gold)">Improve Your Game</p>
        <a href="/improve-your-golf-game/">Improvement Hub</a>
